Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:16.64,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:20.75,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,This slave here is my recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:28.42,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,It's level 75.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:31.57,Main,N,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's close to twenty times my level.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:33.46,Main,N,0,0,0,,How much for this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:37.71,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Well, it is highly capable in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.71,0:00:40.48,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,How does 15 gold pieces sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:44.18,Main,N,0,0,0,,Showing me your most expensive slave \Nknowing that I can't afford it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:48.58,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Indeed. You're sure to become \None of my best patrons,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:52.36,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,so I need you to develop \Na keen eye, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:54.70,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.73,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen my best,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:01:01.46,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,let me ask you: what kind \Nof slave would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:03.57,Main,N,0,0,0,,One that's cheap and obedient.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:05.91,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:08.12,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,a demi-human?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:12.30,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,These aren't suited for \Ncombat or manual labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:14.72,Main,N,0,0,0,,If I need them in battle, I'll train them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:16.83,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,That's an amusing response,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.83,0:01:19.26,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,when you don't believe in people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:21.79,Main,N,0,0,0,,But slaves aren't people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:24.34,Main,N,0,0,0,,Training one is no different \Nthan upgrading my shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:28.20,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Well, you've got me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.17,0:01:33.50,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,These are the cheapest \Nslaves I can offer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.50,0:01:34.65,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,From the left...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:35.80,Main,N,0,0,0,,Raise your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:45.98,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,That half-raccoon is diseased \Nand has a mental disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:49.02,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,I'm having a real hard time with her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:54.33,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Her previous owner loved \Nhis torture, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:57.60,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,I doubt she'll last much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:01:58.67,Main,N,0,0,0,,I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:01.50,Main,N,0,0,0,,I'll take this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:39.85,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:56.74,Main,N,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:58.44,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Worry not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:00.40,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,The pain will dissipate soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:07.77,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,The slave crest on her chest makes \Nit impossible for her to disobey you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:13.83,Main,N,0,0,0,,"Party member settings"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:17.05,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Now this girl is all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:19.70,Main,N,0,0,0,,Thirty silvers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.87,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,There's one extra in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.46,Main,N,0,0,0,,That's your commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:30.98,Main,N,0,0,0,,You were going to wring it out \Nof me anyway, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:32.61,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Thank you for being so understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:36.13,Main,N,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I should know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.34,Main,N,0,0,0,,Tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.42,Main,N,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:44.17,Main,Raph,0,0,0,,R-Raphtalia...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.22,Main,N,0,0,0,,Raphtalia, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:49.18,Main,N,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:54.69,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to your next visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:00.77,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,So he really did choose her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:03.99,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,This is getting exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:06.99,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:10.49,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:14.37,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... What's with the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.88,Main,N,0,0,0,,Give me a weapon she can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.18,Main,N,0,0,0,,Keep it under six silvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.05,Main,N,0,0,0,,Took you long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.34,Main,R,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:28.84,Main,N,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.59,Main,N,0,0,0,,Raphtalia, draw your knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:38.31,Main,N,0,0,0,,Let me see you stab and burst this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:40.27,Main,R,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.19,Main,N,0,0,0,,This is an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:48.36,Main,N,0,0,0,,You only hurt yourself by refusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:49.69,Main,N,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:56.41,Main,N,0,0,0,,Too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.71,Main,N,0,0,0,,Put more heart in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:05:59.63,Main,N,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.13,Main,N,0,0,0,,Huh? I get EXP, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:13.35,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Probably because you set her as a\Ncompanion when forming the pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:16.93,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Wait, you didn't do that\Nwith the lady from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.02,Main,N,0,0,0,,Damn that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:20.48,Main,N,0,0,0,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:25.78,Main,N,0,0,0,,From here on out, I expect you \Nto fight monsters for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.20,Main,N,0,0,0,,I bought you with what little money I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.74,Main,N,0,0,0,,You'd better help me recoup \Nyour cost, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:35.12,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Kid, it ain't gonna be useful to anybody if she dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.87,Main,N,0,0,0,,Thanks for the compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.42,Main,N,0,0,0,,Quit sitting around. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:42.67,Main,R,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.21,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:50.76,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,I don't know whether it's our country to blame, \Nor if the kid's just gone bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.10,Main,N,0,0,0,,Three silvers left...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.35,Main,Merch,0,0,0,,Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:02.56,Main,Merch,0,0,0,,We don't have all day, you little shits!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.32,Main,Merch,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you, you moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.74,Main,Slave,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.11,Main,N,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.20,Main,R,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.28,Main,N,0,0,0,,You can't fight on an empty stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.20,Main,N,0,0,0,,Let's get some lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.42,Main,R,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1065)}U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.33,Main,N,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1065)}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.25,Main,R,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1065)}This place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.13,Main,N,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1065)}Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:30.04,Main,G,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.55,Main,G,0,0,0,,Ack, it's the Shield Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.14,Main,G,0,0,0,,Is he the rapist?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:35.80,Main,G,0,0,0,,Keep it down! He'll hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.39,Main,N,0,0,0,,Can I order?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.85,Main,G,0,0,0,,Huh? I-I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:40.75,Main,W,0,0,0,,Look, it's a demi-human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:42.44,Main,G,0,0,0,,Why's a demi here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.19,Main,N,0,0,0,,The cheapest lunch set you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.06,Main,G,0,0,0,,Someone kick her out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.23,Main,N,0,0,0,,And she'll have whatever that kid's having.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.74,Main,G,0,0,0,,That'll be nine coppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:50.40,Main,N,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.41,Main,R,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:57.49,Main,N,0,0,0,,Did you want something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:01.33,Main,R,0,0,0,,Why are you getting it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.63,Main,N,0,0,0,,Because you looked like \Nyou wanted to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.00,Main,G,0,0,0,,Here's your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.59,Main,N,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:15.55,Main,R,0,0,0,,Can I really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.06,Main,N,0,0,0,,Yes, just eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.28,Main,N,0,0,0,,Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:46.54,Main,N,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.25,Main,R,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.89,Main,N,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still don't taste a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.44,Main,N,0,0,0,,Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:02.05,Main,R,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.56,Main,N,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.78,Main,N,0,0,0,,Blending ability, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.66,Main,N,0,0,0,,That might come in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.62,Main,R,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.71,Main,R,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.92,Main,N,0,0,0,,A hero. The shield one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:36.13,Main,R,0,0,0,,You mean... One of the Four Cardinal Heroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:36.67,Main,N,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.39,Main,RDad,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raphtalia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:43.85,Main,RDad,0,0,0,,Do you know of the four legendary heroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:47.98,Main,R,0,0,0,,Yep! The ones with the sword, \Nthe bow, and the spear...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.73,Main,R,0,0,0,,And then, the one with the shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:50.94,Main,RDad,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:56.24,Main,RDad,0,0,0,,The Shield Hero, in particular, \Ntreated us demi-humans very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:59.20,Main,R,0,0,0,,Really? I'd like to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:02.83,Main,RMom,0,0,0,,If you're a good girl, I'm sure \Nyou'll meet him one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:12.34,Main,R,0,0,0,,The Shield Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.76,Main,R,0,0,0,,U-Um... What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.84,Main,N,0,0,0,,Iwatani Naofumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.80,Main,R,0,0,0,,Iwatani... Naofumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.30,Main,N,0,0,0,,Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.73,Main,N,0,0,0,,It's a medicine I blended.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:28.52,Main,N,0,0,0,,Apparently, it can cure mild colds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:30.35,Main,N,0,0,0,,Drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:36.69,Main,R,0,0,0,,So bitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.95,Main,N,0,0,0,,Good medicine tastes bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:39.82,Main,N,0,0,0,,Just drink it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.64,Main,RDad,0,0,0,,We're sorry, Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:10.23,Main,RMom,0,0,0,,We want you to live, Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:13.15,Main,RMom,0,0,0,,Please forgive our selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.77,Main,R,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.62,Main,R,0,0,0,,Dad! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:25.70,Main,N,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:27.41,Main,N,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:30.04,Main,R,0,0,0,,No... Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:29.12,Main,N,0,0,0,,Just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:35.29,Main,R,0,0,0,,No! Dad, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:33.58,Main,N,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:36.92,Main,N,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.88,Main,N,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.81,Main,Herbist,0,0,0,,The quality's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:51.10,Main,Herbist,0,0,0,,Are you well versed in\N making medicines, Sir Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.40,Main,N,0,0,0,,Yesterday was my first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.56,Main,Herbist,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:57.52,Main,N,0,0,0,,Which is more profitable, \Nselling herbs or medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:02.28,Main,Herbist,0,0,0,,Due to the Wave's impact,\N medicine is flying off the shelves lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.49,Main,Herbist,0,0,0,,so I'd pay more for medicine than for herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:06.62,Main,N,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:11.00,Main,Herbist,0,0,0,,In total, this is worth four silvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:14.25,Main,N,0,0,0,,Say, do you have any tools \Nyou don't use anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:15.75,Main,Kid1,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:16.46,Main,Kid2,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.63,Main,Kid1,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:18.67,Main,N,0,0,0,,Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:18.67,Main,Kid1,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:21.88,Main,N,0,0,0,,Do you want one of those balls?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.80,Main,R,0,0,0,,N-Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:27.35,Main,R,0,0,0,,I don't want it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.85,Main,N,0,0,0,,{\i1}So she wants one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.51,Main,N,0,0,0,,You can play with it {\i1}after{\i0}\Nwe're done with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:38.82,Main,R,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.24,Main,G,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.53,Main,G,0,0,0,,Uh, the Shield Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.07,Main,N,0,0,0,,I'd like to rent a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.45,Main,N,0,0,0,,My companion might scream at night, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:52.25,Main,N,0,0,0,,You {\i1}will{\i0} let us stay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.79,Main,G,0,0,0,,O-Of course! I'll prepare a room at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:04.34,Main,N,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to find a way to survive before \Nthe next Wave of Catastrophe hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:41.34,Main,N,0,0,0,,All right. We can go a little \Ndeeper into the forest now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:46.88,Main,N,0,0,0,,A rabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:48.22,Main,N,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:51.39,Main,N,0,0,0,,Now, Raphtalia! Stab it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:55.43,Main,N,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Get on with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:58.60,Main,R,0,0,0,,B-But... It'll bleed if I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.65,Main,N,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.39,Main,R,0,0,0,,I'm scared of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.99,Main,N,0,0,0,,Listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:10.70,Main,N,0,0,0,,If you can't fight, then I \Nwon't be able to look after you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:15.37,Main,N,0,0,0,,A Wave that threatens the world's \Nexistence is coming soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:18.54,Main,N,0,0,0,,I have to get as strong \Nas I can before it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:21.88,Main,N,0,0,0,,But defense is all I'm good for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:24.34,Main,N,0,0,0,,I need someone to fight for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.68,Main,N,0,0,0,,If you can't do it, I'll get someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:30.26,Main,N,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:32.89,Main,R,0,0,0,,You're going to fight the Catastrophe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.64,Main,N,0,0,0,,That is my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.35,Main,R,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:54.83,Main,R,0,0,0,,Master... I'll fight for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:58.00,Main,R,0,0,0,,So please don't throw me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:14:59.58,Main,N,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.58,Main,N,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:04.46,Main,N,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:08.01,Main,N,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I want to live, I have \Nno choice but to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:12.39,Main,N,0,0,0,,Sell us a new weapon for this amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:16.60,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Time to get the little miss a sword, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:20.94,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,One on the short side would \Nbe good to start off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:22.73,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.69,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,It's a short sword made of iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:26.28,Main,N,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:30.20,Main,N,0,0,0,,Is there a town or village nearby that \Nwe can travel to with our equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:36.20,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Well, with your stuff, it'd have to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.54,Main,N,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:45.17,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Around two silvers in all, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.50,Main,N,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:50.84,Main,N,0,0,0,,Hey, do you know of any spots nearby \Nwhen you can earn a lot of money quick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.26,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:57.93,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The ores from that coal pit over there \Nshould fetch a decent amount, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.88,Main,N,0,0,0,,Is there a catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:04.81,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Ever since the first Wave, it's become \Nhome to a bunch of dangerous monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:07.40,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Nobody dares approach it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.69,Main,N,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:13.20,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Sheesh! I don't know what our \Nsummoned "heroes" are even doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:25.71,Main,N,0,0,0,,It's got an exclusive effect and skill, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:33.63,Main,N,0,0,0,,Rope Shield... Not exactly\Nwhat I'd call a creative name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.05,Main,N,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.68,Main,N,0,0,0,,Air Strike Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:46.48,Main,R,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.40,Main,N,0,0,0,,It's nothing. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:59.03,Main,N,0,0,0,,There are dangerous \Nmonsters here, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:01.04,Main,N,0,0,0,,The moment things go south, we run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.54,Main,N,0,0,0,,You'd better keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:03.21,Main,R,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:05.67,Main,R,0,0,0,,U...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:06.75,Main,R,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:07.63,Main,N,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:12.30,Main,R,0,0,0,,How should I address you, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.72,Main,N,0,0,0,,Call me whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:15.43,Main,R,0,0,0,,Th-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.10,Main,N,0,0,0,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:23.98,Main,N,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.35,Main,R,0,0,0,,Are those...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:33.90,Main,N,0,0,0,,This will fetch a pretty penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.36,Main,N,0,0,0,,Raphtalia, let's try over there next...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.54,Main,R,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:03.14,Main,N,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:05.39,Main,R,0,0,0,,D-Dog monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:09.86,Main,R,0,0,0,,Killed all the villagers, \Neven Dad and Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.65,Main,N,0,0,0,,During the first Wave, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:16.15,Main,N,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's why she starts \Ncrying every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.79,Main,N,0,0,0,,Is that the same dog that \Nkilled your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:27.50,Main,R,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.62,Main,N,0,0,0,,Listen, Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:32.50,Main,N,0,0,0,,Take that thing out here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:36.22,Main,N,0,0,0,,If you fight and make me stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:39.89,Main,N,0,0,0,,we can fend off the Waves of Catastrophe \Nand prevent that tragedy from reoccurring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.01,Main,N,0,0,0,,Your parents won't ever come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:47.85,Main,N,0,0,0,,But we can prevent other kids \Nfrom going through what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:53.69,Main,N,0,0,0,,And all I'm capable of is making \Nsure you can fight as best you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.87,Main,N,0,0,0,,Now, Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.54,Main,N,0,0,0,,Stab it with your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:05.45,Main,N,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.45,Main,R,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:12.13,Main,N,0,0,0,,If I die, so will you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:12.96,Main,R,0,0,0,,Please no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.96,Main,N,0,0,0,,Then hurry up and kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:17.63,Main,N,0,0,0,,This is an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:34.69,Main,N,0,0,0,,Raphtalia, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:38.32,Main,N,0,0,0,,If you can't fight, then get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.65,Main,R,0,0,0,,But what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:43.66,Main,N,0,0,0,,I'll buy time for you to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:44.91,Main,R,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:50.12,Main,R,0,0,0,,That'd be just like then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:52.58,Main,N,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.00,Main,R,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:56.67,Main,N,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:58.76,Main,N,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:04.93,Main,N,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:08.77,Main,N,0,0,0,,Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:17.32,Main,N,0,0,0,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:27.20,Main,N,0,0,0,,Air Strike Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:29.95,Main,N,0,0,0,,Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.68,Main,N,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:50.35,Main,R,0,0,0,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:55.85,Main,N,0,0,0,,Hey, even with the shield's power,\N the wound still hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:59.81,Main,R,0,0,0,,Don't ever die! Please don't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:01.69,Main,R,0,0,0,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.65,Main,N,0,0,0,,{\i1}She chose my name, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:07.66,Main,N,0,0,0,,You attack, and I defend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:10.45,Main,N,0,0,0,,That way, neither of us will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:11.79,Main,R,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:15.67,Main,N,0,0,0,,We're leaving once I feed \Nthis monster to my shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:18.09,Main,R,0,0,0,,Okay, Naofumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:21.55,Main,N,0,0,0,,Get off already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:23.51,Main,R,0,0,0,,A bit longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:04.27,Main,N,0,0,0,,The ore made us a lot of money, \Nso you can eat all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:05.16,Main,R,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:08.15,Main,N,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:09.07,Main,R,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:10.91,Main,N,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.15,0:23:16.15,Main,R,0,0,0,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.17,0:23:20.57,Main,R,0,0,0,,Let's survive, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.57,0:23:22.21,Main,N,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:27.55,Main,N,0,0,0,,Here. A kids' lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:30.34,Main,N,0,0,0,,isn't complete without this.
